---

<section id="story" class="section story-bg">
	<div class="container">
		<div style="text-align: center; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
			<h2 class="section-title fade-in-up">The Coach Behind it all...</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="grid-2 story-content fade-in-up delay-100">
			
			<div class="story-image-wrap">
				<img src="/coach.jpg" alt="Salakawy Coach" class="story-image" loading="lazy" />
			</div>
			
			<div class="story-text">
				<h3>Turning Fitness into a Lifestyle</h3>
				<p>
					Since 2021, I've helped <strong>over 11,000 people</strong> transform their bodies. 
					My mission is to show you that <strong>you can achieve greatness</strong> without starving yourself. But you have to <strong>take control now</strong>.
				</p>
				<p>
					I don't just provide a set of recipes or exercises; I help you rewrite the way you think about food, training, and yourself. 
					<strong>True progress doesn't start in the gym... It starts when you make a decision</strong>.
				</p>
				<p>
					Anyone can follow a plan for a week, but my goal is to help you build the <strong>mental resilience</strong> to stop making excuses. It's time to put down the junk food, hit the weights, and <strong>claim your transformation</strong>. 
					A diet plan you can get anywhere, but what I offer is a permanent <span class="sparkle-text">lifestyle shift</span>.
				</p>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.story-bg {
		background-color: var(--surface-color);
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.story-content {
		align-items: center;
		gap: 4rem;
	}

	.story-image-wrap {
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
	}

	.story-image-wrap::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
		box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.story-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
		filter: brightness(0.9) contrast(1.1);
		transition: transform var(--transition);
	}

	.story-image-wrap:hover .story-image {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	.story-text h3 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--accent-color);
	}

	.story-text p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.story-text p strong {
		color: var(--text-main);
	}

    /* Sparkle Text Effect */
    .sparkle-text {
        color: var(--accent-color);
        font-weight: 700;
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .sparkle-text::before, .sparkle-text::after {
        content: "✨";
        position: absolute;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: text-sparkle 2s infinite;
    }

    .sparkle-text::before {
        top: -10px;
        left: -10px;
        animation-delay: 0.5s;
    }

    .sparkle-text::after {
        bottom: -5px;
        right: -15px;
        animation-delay: 1.2s;
    }

    @keyframes text-sparkle {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0) rotate(0deg); }
        50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.2) rotate(20deg); }
    }

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.story-content {
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.story-text h3 {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .story-text p {
            text-align: center;
        }
	}
</style>
